  "description": {
   "en": "Because of his naturally scary face, 35-year-old Kitakaze Tatsuo has never received a Valentine’s chocolate from a woman. His female co-workers avoid him, and people on the street fear him.  \n  \nOnly the beautiful office lady Miharu Chisa is kind to him and always smiles at Tatsuo. After helping her one day, a teary-eyed Miharu gives Tatsuo a Valentine’s chocolate! He believes it’s just obligation chocolate, but when he opens it, an “I Love You” is written there! Could this finally be the beginning of a blossoming romance in Tatsuo’s wintry life, or…!?"
